# =============================================================================
# Explicit public-docs guard
# =============================================================================
# /docs/benchmarks/ is the public-facing competitive-benchmark hub — dated
# canonical reports, archive, hub README, reproduction scripts. This
# directory MUST stay tracked. The negation below is defensive: if a future
# gitignore rule ever matches /docs/benchmarks/* (e.g. someone adds
# /docs/*/ or a broader pattern), this keeps the hub checked in.
!/docs/benchmarks/
!/docs/benchmarks/**

# =============================================================================
# Local-only spec/prompt files
# =============================================================================
/prompts/
INTENT_PROMPT.md
INTENT_PROMPT_V2.md
INTENT_SPEC_FAANG_CORE_INFRA.mdconsole
crates/uffs-cli/console
